#: ../../02-usage.rst:175
msgid "并行分词"
msgstr "Parallel Segmentation"

#: ../../02-usage.rst:177
msgid "原理：将目标文本按行分隔后，把各行文本分配到多个 Python 进程并行分词， 然后归并结果，从而获得分词速度的可观提升"
msgstr "Principle: After splitting the target text by lines, the lines are distributed to multiple Python processes for parallel segmentation, and then the results are merged, resulting in a significant increase in segmentation speed."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:178
msgid "基于 python 自带的 ``multiprocessing`` 模块，目前暂不支持 Windows"
msgstr "Based on Python's built-in ``multiprocessing`` module; currently not supported on Windows."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:179
msgid "用法："
msgstr "Usage:"

#: ../../02-usage.rst:180
msgid "`jieba.enable_parallel(4)` # 开启并行分词模式，参数为并行进程数"
msgstr "`jieba.enable_parallel(4)` # Enable parallel segmentation mode; the parameter is the number of parallel processes."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:181
msgid "`jieba.disable_parallel()` # 关闭并行分词模式"
msgstr "`jieba.disable_parallel()` # Disable parallel segmentation mode."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:182
msgid ""
"例子：\\ "
"https://github.com/fxsjy/jieba/blob/master/test/parallel/test_file.py"
msgstr ""
"Example: "
"https://github.com/fxsjy/jieba/blob/master/test/parallel/test_file.py"

#: ../../02-usage.rst:183
msgid "实验结果：在 4 核 3.4GHz Linux 机器上，对金庸全集进行精确分词， 获得了 1MB/s 的速度，是单进程版的 3.3 倍。"
msgstr "Experimental results: On a 4-core 3.4GHz Linux machine, precise segmentation of the complete works of Jin Yong achieved a speed of 1MB/s, which is 3.3 times that of the single-process version."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:184
msgid "**注意**\\ ：并行分词仅支持默认分词器 ``jieba.dt`` 和 ``jieba.posseg.dt``\\ 。"
msgstr "**Note**: Parallel segmentation only supports the default tokenizers ``jieba.dt`` and ``jieba.posseg.dt``."

