msgstr "Lazy Loading Mechanism"

#: ../../02-usage.rst:241
msgid ""
"``jieba`` 采用延迟加载，\\ ``import jieba`` 和 ``jieba.Tokenizer()`` 不会立即触发词典的加载，"
" 一旦有必要才开始加载词典构建前缀字典。如果你想手工初始 ``jieba`` ，也可以手动初始化。"
msgstr "``jieba`` uses lazy loading; ``import jieba`` and ``jieba.Tokenizer()`` will not immediately trigger dictionary loading. The dictionary will only be loaded to build the prefix dictionary when necessary. If you want to initialize ``jieba`` manually, you can do so."

#: ../../02-usage.rst:244
msgid "在 0.28 之前的版本是不能指定主词典的路径的，有了延迟加载机制后， 你可以改变主词典的路径:"
msgstr "In versions prior to 0.28, the path to the main dictionary could not be specified. With the lazy loading mechanism, you can now change the path to the main dictionary:"

